858
01:02:33,240 --> 01:02:36,759
ABOUT OTHER ASPECTS
OF OUR CULTURE.

859
01:02:36,780 --> 01:02:40,000
THERE ARE 6,000 DIFFERENT
LANGUAGES SPOKEN TODAY

860
01:02:40,20 --> 01:02:42,930
AROUND THE WORLD.

861
01:02:42,950 --> 01:02:46,69
